title: 2 Pack Pull out Cabinet Organizer Expandable Slide out Drawers,Heavy Duty Pull Out Drawers for Cabinets,No Drill Roll Out Shelf Adhesive,Adjustable Width 12.6"-20"
description: Description:【PULL OUT DESIGN】This pull-out organizer fits well in the kitchen cabinet, with a smooth and quiet sliding system, allowing you to easily and quickly access items deep in the cabinet, maximizing the cabinet storage space.【EXPANDABLE DESIGN】This pull-out cabinet organizer can expand the width of about 32-50 cm/12.6-19.69 inch, which can adapt to kitchen cabinets of different sizes, and the depth is about 42 cm/16.54 inch.
